 Buhari was represented at the event by the Minister of Agriculture and Rural Development, Alhaji Sabo Nanono at the commissioning and Handing Over Ceremony of Erosion Control Works at Faruruwa Ward Road, Takai Local Government Area of Kano State. Photo; TWITTER/FMARDNG  He assured that no part of the country would suffer any neglect owing to its geographical location or political consideration. Buhari gave the assurance during the commissioning and handing over of the erosion control works at the Faruruwa Bridge in Takai Council of Kano State, executed by the Ecological Fund Office under the Office of the Secretary to the Government of the Federation (OSGF) at the weekend. He was represented at the event by the Minister of Agriculture and Rural Development, Alhaji Sabo Nanono. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .